    <section id="overview">
      <h2>OLSP Live Profit Builders Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p>Live Profit Builders sits as the first significant paid subscription tier above the $7 one-time Megalink purchase, and below Community Builders and Team Builders in the OLSP upgrade ladder. Its core proposition is expanding how and when you earn from referred leads: rather than earning only when a lead makes a purchase, LPB members reportedly earn when their leads attend a live event or complete onboarding training steps — not just when they buy.</p>

      <h3>What's Included (Vendor and Affiliate Claims)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Mega Live Link:</strong> an upgraded version of the standard MegaLink that automatically routes prospects into the current live event, challenge, or funnel running in the OLSP ecosystem at the time they click.</li>
        <li><strong>100% front-end commissions</strong> on designated MegaLink offers (e.g., the $7 entry product).</li>
        <li><strong>$1 per unique verified attendee</strong> at specific Tuesday and Saturday live events linked to the LPB funnel.</li>
        <li><strong>Lifetime account-level attribution:</strong> once a lead signs up via your link, future OLSP purchases from that lead are attributed to you — not to a browser cookie with an expiry date.</li>
        <li><strong>Lead activation bonuses:</strong> referred leads can earn $5 for each of their first four completed OLSP onboarding training sessions, incentivizing engagement with the system and keeping leads active.</li>
        <li><strong>AI Marketing Material Generator:</strong> produces emails, social media posts, captions, and scripts "in the member's voice" for each upcoming live event, reducing manual copywriting time.</li>
        <li><strong>Traffic challenges:</strong> structured 30-day and shorter programs including the 30-Day Traffic Challenge, Commission Challenge, Student Challenge, and AI Twin Challenge.</li>
        <li><strong>Live Premium Action Plans:</strong> done-for-you promotional blueprints for each upcoming live event — what to post, when to post, how to drive attendance.</li>
        <li><strong>Private LPB community</strong> inside the OLSP platform (separate from the public Facebook group), with peer support and strategy sharing.</li>
        <li><strong>Viral Hub credits</strong> for amplifying content across platforms.</li>
        <li><strong>Leaderboard and points system</strong> with recognition and occasional cash prizes linked to activity and results.</li>
      </ul>

